#: ../dev_guide/python_style_guide.rst:92 ../dev_guide/python_style_guide.rst:349
#: ../dev_guide/python_style_guide.rst:378 ../dev_guide/python_style_guide.rst:397
#: ../dev_guide/python_style_guide.rst:410
